Winning numbers drawn in 'MassCash' game
07 Nov 2019, 04:23 by The Associated Press
BRAINTREE, Mass. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Wednesday evening's drawing of the Massachusetts Lottery's "MassCash" game were:
02-14-21-22-35
(two, fourteen, twenty-one, twenty-two, thirty-five)
